      "role": "user",
      "content": "That's a strong start, really captures that condescending tone. Can you expand on that? Maybe a bit more about how he views their social structure compared to his own—like, how he sees their way of living vs. the \"proper\" way of doing things? Just to really hammer home that contrast for the scene.",
